    "data_flow_integrity": "Unclear what happens if SendGrid accepts the email (200) but the subsequent DB write to persist the delivery record fails. This is a critical consistency gap — the email is sent but the system has no record of it. Needs a defined strategy: at-least-once delivery record persistence or an explicit reconciliation mechanism."
