        "scenario": "Database connection pool exhaustion or outage",
        "handling": "unhandled",
        "recommendation": "Define behavior: should emails still be sent if DB is down? If yes, buffer delivery records for later persistence. If no, fail fast. Either way, the health check must reflect DB health so traffic is routed away."
