      "reason": "The job queue is a critical integration point with zero observability. No queue depth metric, no consumer lag metric, no dead-letter queue, and no alerting. A poisoned message or slow consumer will silently delay all email delivery with no signal to the on-call engineer. Need queue_depth gauge, consumer_lag gauge, and dead-letter queue with alerting.",
      "routed_to": "Coach K"
